    "description": "The Qube Secure Media Block is used in Digital Cinema applications, providing core functionality required to playback Digital Cinema Packages. The module performs essence decryption when processing encrypted content, it ensures link encryption downstream to a projector device, and it provides other features as to enable a fully capable Digital Cinema Server. Content owners and other stake holders rely upon the security features provided by the Qube Secure Media Block to protect their valuable content, and to perform secure logging of operations within a theatre auditorium.",
